        "children": [
          {
            "type": "accordion-item",
            "props": {
              "summary": "What’s the difference between  development programs and  entry-level roles?",
              "classes_defaultOpen": false,
              "cq:lastRolledout": "Tue Jun 16 2026 09:04:50 GMT+0000",
              "text": "<p>Development programs include rotations, structured learning, and mentorship, while entry-level roles place you directly into a specific full-time position.</p>",
              "cq:lastRolledoutBy": "sheetal.joshi@abbvie.com"
            },
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "type": "accordion-item",
            "props": {
              "summary": "Can I apply to more than one program or role?",
              "classes_defaultOpen": false,
              "cq:lastRolledout": "Tue Jun 16 2026 09:04:50 GMT+0000",
              "text": "<p>Yes, you can apply to multiple roles that align with your skills and interests.</p>",
              "cq:lastRolledoutBy": "sheetal.joshi@abbvie.com"
            },
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "type": "accordion-item",
            "props": {
              "summary": "Are AbbVie's student and new graduate programs global?",
              "classes_defaultOpen": false,
              "cq:lastRolledout": "Tue Jun 16 2026 09:04:50 GMT+0000",
              "text": "<p>Some programs, like operations and finance, offer global rotations. Others are U.S.-based, but may lead to global rotations over time. Check out our <a href=\"https://careers.abbvie.com/en\" title=\"career site opens in a new window.\">career site</a> for more specific information on roles within your country of interest.</p>",
              "cq:lastRolledoutBy": "sheetal.joshi@abbvie.com"
            },
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "type": "accordion-item",
            "props": {
              "summary": "Does AbbVie offer relocation support for development programs and entry-level roles?",
              "classes_defaultOpen": false,
              "cq:lastRolledout": "Tue Jun 16 2026 09:04:50 GMT+0000",
              "text": "<p>Relocation offerings are dependent on the candidate's role and eligibility.</p>",
              "cq:lastRolledoutBy": "sheetal.joshi@abbvie.com"
            },
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "type": "accordion-item",
            "props": {
              "summary": "What is the AbbVie interview process like?",
              "classes_defaultOpen": false,
              "cq:lastRolledout": "Tue Jun 16 2026 09:04:50 GMT+0000",
              "text": "<p>You may go through phone or video interviews, with a mix of behavioral, technical, or case-style questions based on the role.</p>",
              "cq:lastRolledoutBy": "sheetal.joshi@abbvie.com"
            },
            "children": []
          }
        ]
